<DATELINE>SWAN LAKE, N.Y. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Former President Richard Nixon gave an
encouraging talk to several hundred drug rehabilitation patients,
then sat down at the piano.
   Nixon played ``God Bless America'' and ``Happy Birthday'' during
his visit to a Daytop Village Foundation residential drug treatment
center Wednesday to mark the foundation's 25th anniversary.
