propose to buy out the company for about $75 a share.
   That prompted buying of such other tobacco stocks as American
Brands, up 2~ at 57[, and Philip Morris, up 2} at 96}. Philip
Morris is itself in the process of going after Kraft, which traded
today at 89~, down {.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks rose
.73 to 156.91. At the American Stock Exchange, the market value
index was up .43 at 304.91.
</TEXT>
